									<h2>The Solution</h2>
									<p> We chose Android since it is a popular platform and supports java. This means we could use  Java Robot, which simulates keypresses on your computer with certain given data. Creating a server with Java, the idea is to setup a port connection between the phone and the computer first. Then, using buttons, the phone can send data over to the server.  </p>
